de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class SingleMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.SingleMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SingleMode>

    public class SingleMode
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<SingleMode>
    That objects are used to represents the intern objects like answers, questions. The single mode objects are displayed in the mail inbox. The operator can set the filter(combo boxes settings) that constrains the objects that are displayed.
